name: Nut
description: $Nut isn’t just a token; it’s a vibe. Inspired by the poker term “nut hand” (the strongest hand you can hold), $Nut takes that unbeatable energy and injects it into the crypto market. It’s built on the Solana blockchain, making it fast, cheap, and scalable — basically the opposite of gas-fee hell. The Token, the meme, the movement, the vibe, the legend, THE NUT. A no brainer for degens who play to win. Here every HODLer is a legend, a nuthead. $Nut is the play that makes jeets cry and degens grin.
